data.description: Welcome to your lakeside sanctuary on almost 2 acres of pristine beauty! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence with a BRAND NEW ROOF is a true gem nestled among tranquil surroundings that allows room to roam. Boasting an expansive lot with lush greenery and lake views, this home offers a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and outdoor serenity. As you enter the residence, you are greeted by a spacious and open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen features upgraded appliances, granite counter-tops, and ample cabinet space. The large bay window provides abundant natural light.This home features two master suites, each offering a private upscale bathroom. One of the master suites is over-sized with vaulted ceilings and adorned with a cozy fireplace. This suite has 2 separate walk-in closets, and a large luxurious bathroom with a garden tub. The remaining three bedrooms are generously sized, offering comfort and flexibility for guests or family members. The in-ground pool, surrounded by a spacious patio with outdoor shower and kitchen area are perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the beautiful weather. The expansive backyard leads to the private lakefront, providing a tranquil retreat.The property includes a massive 1800 sqft workshop with RV storage, offering endless possibilities for creative pursuits or extra storage space. This versatile addition adds value and convenience to this already extraordinary property. Don't miss the opportunity to make this outstanding property your own – a true retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life but conveniently LESS THAN 10 MINUTES FROM THE VILLAGES with shopping, restaurants and doctors
